metadata.title: RZ/V: Cannot access the latest version AI SDK Website

sections.content:
Question:
I could access old version AI SDK website only when I access from a search engine. 
Answer:
the latest version AI SDK website URL is below
https://renesas-rz.github.io/rzv_ai_sdk/latest/
You can always access the latest page from this URL.
